03-04T15:34:24.000Z","msg":"係咪即係印度已大爆發"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-03-04T15:36:03.000Z","msg":"今日增加左16宗, 同意大利團有關, 總共印度有28宗<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/arrested.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/heard.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-03-04T15:37:59.000Z","msg":"睇下黎緊外國有幾多 「去完印度中招」的確診個案先<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n話唔定印度而家爆撚度武漢咁，但都唔識封城<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/369.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-03-04T15:40:50.000Z","msg":"<strong>16名義大利遊客確診！<span style=\"color: red;\">印度感染人數飆升至28例</span></strong><br />\n<br />\n新冠肺炎（COVID-19）疫情擴散全球，其中印度衛生部4日突然宣布，一團來自義大利的旅行團的21人當中，有16人確診，令印度當地累計確診人數飆升至28例。為了防止疫情蔓延，印度即日起將擴大之前的入境篩查範圍，在所有機場以及海陸口岸對所有入境旅客測量體溫。<br />\n<br />\n綜合外媒報導，印度衛生與福利部部長瓦爾第（Harsh Vardhan）4日指出，一名義大利遊客日前跟團來印度觀光，不料他與妻子紛紛確診，而與他接觸的21名義大利遊客中，也有16人確診感染新冠肺炎。目前，印度確診人數飆升至28例。<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://www.ettoday.net/news/20200304/1659880.htm\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ettoday.net%2Fnews%2F20200304%2F1659880.htm&d=%2BOqOIcZVGdgLhUso5zZbIPS0i%2BS8%2FYHgnNJfWlbrK%2Bw%3D&h=ca60d1ba\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://www.ettoday.net/news/20200304/1659880.htm</a>"},{"pid":"0f87dd7c78612f7b7837740c432516552ef49ccc","tid":1910390,"uid":220697,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"fb478e8b3165b66d26214a8696452a972b6434e7","tid":1910390,"uid":17646,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"quote":{"pid":"75e5a2e8bdf34f1c274cfd6883239b8f880ca3d8","tid":1910390,"uid":212626,"like":9,"dislike":0,"score":9,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2020-03-04T15:27:21.000Z","msg":"印度輸入個案<img src=\"/assets/faces/fs/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-03-04T15:27:55.000Z","msg":"聖水無用啦"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-03-04T15:44:38.000Z","msg":"冇食咖哩"},{"pid":"67a4822ac06501fde3b9676a16bf9351a08c4c17","tid":1910390,"uid":4349,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"e125aa1733a6a0eeba660620f20da28fd9